titlestmt.titleproper: A Guide to the Russell Sage Foundation records, SG 3 FA413

profiledesc.creation: This finding aid was produced using ArchivesSpace on 2025-04-01 04:03:58 UTC.

did.unittitle: Russell Sage Foundation records, SG 3

processinfo.head: Processing Information
processinfo.p: Enhanced Access - Multi-Level Access. Intermediate preservation actions. Most records remain in original file folders.
Processing is ongoing and material will be added to this finding aid as records are opened for research.

acqinfo.head: Immediate Source of Acquisition
acqinfo.p: Russell Sage Foundation records donated to Rockefeller Archive Center by Eric Wanner, RSF President, April 2010.

userestrict.head: Conditions Governing Use
userestrict.p: Rockefeller Archive Center holds title, copyright and literary rights in the collection, in so far as it holds them, and has authority to grant permission to cite and publish archival material from the collection.

accessrestrict.head: Conditions Governing Access
accessrestrict.p: Records 15 years old or older are open for research, with select materials restricted as noted. Brittle or damaged items are available at the discretion of the RAC.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: Grant administration records including grant letter, budget, correspondence, reports, and associated publications or grant products.
